parameters: Can't I just go out the back?
It's already locked up. Use the front.
I knew it. That wasn't even a gun.
Just a drill with the bit removed.
Not very convincing, but it bought me a few seconds anyway.
You may know why you’re here.
Not a god damn clue, man.
I feel like shit. What did you do?
I don’t know what you’re talking about.
You were the only front of house male staff at Whang’s Kitchen and Bakery two Wednesday evenings ago.
I'm telling you. I don’t know any Angels, and I don’t know you.
Fine. Commit any sex offenses lately?
"Lately"? I haven't seen her in, like, six months.
She quit a long time ago.
We got drunk, hooked up, and then she decided she regretted it later.
She got a good lawyer and got me put on probation. End of story.
\.\.So you have a prior conviction for sexual assault.
She just made shit up because—\.\.I don’t know. She’s crazy.
Okay. We're not talking about six months ago. Let’s try this a different way.
Did you have\.\. relations\.\. with anyone in the past two weeks?
Past two weeks\..\..\.. uhh.\.\. Two or three people, probably.\| Yeah, two.\| Yes.
.\..\..\.Your current coworker.\.\. 5 feet tall.\.\. Colored hair.
I dunno what lies she fed you, but she never said no or stop or nothing.
What the hell is actually going on?
How are you waving drills around and tying me up and shit over a girl whose name you don’t even pronounce right?
She didn’t tell me she had a boyfriend or nothing, either. Okay?
Nothing you have said has changed my mind in the slightest.
I was going to see if you can transorbitally lobotomize a person with a drill.
I thought I might want to experiment.
Maybe a total glossectomy, or the human equivalent of debarking.
Something along those lines for that\.\. disgusting\.\. mouth of yours.
It's not often you get the chance to dissect a living person. With no anaesthesia, at that.
But I don't even want to touch you.
Pick a letter. C, T, or L.
Do it, and I'll let you go.
Now pick a number between 2 and 7.
C\V[1]. Great. That’s the cervical vertebrae I’m going to drill into your spinal cord above.
Now pick a number between 1 and 12.
T\V[1]. Great. That’s the thoracic vertebrae I’m going to drill into your spinal cord above.
Now pick a number between 1 and 5.
L\V[1]. Great. That’s the lumbar vertebrae I’m going to drill into your spinal cord above.
Then I'll unbind you, and you'll be free to escape.
Good luck making it up the stairs with a detached spinal cord.
Although there is plenty in your system to kill you without medical intervention.
You're free to try. I will kick you back down the stairs if you make it to the top.
"No" was never a choice that was going to be afforded to you.
You will spend your last hours immobilized, helpless, and in a great deal of pain.
